                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p></div><div class="sources"><h3>Events</h3><p class="indent">Mar Samuel,
                            prior to founding Mar
                                Samuel Convent, visited the Convent of John
                                Urtaya.  <a href="/10510-112" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p><hr/><p class="indent">Mar
                            Samuel stood on a column for a time before he began to build
                            his convent. Abraham
                                III sent his monks to help Mar Samuel build the
                            convent.  <a href="/10510-113" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
